The lack of snow in mountain hoteliers
The tracks are not a problem that operators of ski lifts.
The lack of snow discourages people to book their stays in hotels and pensions.
It is always possible to find free rooms for all dates in winter, including Christmas and New Year.
We have a lot of hits on our site.
Internet users roam the offers, asking prices but dare not commit to reserve for the moment.
And if they call, they ask immediately if there will be snow or mud at Christmas, " said Martin Jandura, operator of the information portal Spindl. Info.
If you want to spend the New Year of his dreams to Špindlerův Mlýn, better not too reluctant to book.
If the priority is given to economies and that the quality of accommodation only then, then we can try to wait a few more days.
The Špindler hotel offer for the moment that stays of a week for the New Year.
I think they will try one more time of the place, but they also and accept shorter periods.
And then the number of rooms free will rapidly diminish, " said Jandura.
The tourism agency Ingtours of Vrchlabí also proposes free beds for all periods of winter.
The week of Christmas we are most concerned for the moment, it is not completely sold.
There are still free, say, half of the rooms in our offer.
That is why we have already prepared a few last - minute Christmas stays cheaper, " said the director of Ingtours Petr Schiefert.
The agency Vrchlabí tourism may also propose the New Year to Krkonoše, but there are fewer empty seats.
The first 14 days of February go well, the remaining winter trips are moderately.
This year, the interest in the winter has been negatively influenced by the fact that there is still no snow to Krkonoše.
People expect it to fall.
Nobody wants to spend the winter in the mountain without snow.
If the overlap during the week, Christmas also will be complete, " think Schiefert.
Conversely, the occupation of the hotel in Pec pod Sněžkou is slightly higher than last year.
It was an improvement of about five percent.
We have few places for the New Year as for Christmas.
There is a great interest during the holidays in January and February of Polish sells well too, " said Karel Rada, director of the best hotel in Pec.
The Omnia Hotel near the central park Jánské Lázně is also full to 80 percent during the period of the New Year.
On the contrary, half of the beds are empty at Christmas in the most recent Jánské hotel Lázně.
This year, we were pleasantly surprised by the month of January, where we have already sixty percent of occupation at the moment.
February is a bit lower for the moment, but as soon as the snow will fall, the interest for stays in the Krkonoše grows certainly said the director of the hotel Omnia, Erik Sporysch.
The hotel of Krkonoše should not expect more snow.
On Thursday it will be fresher and if there is, they should be the mountains.
But the time should warm, informed Jiří Jakubský of the Czech Hydrometeorological Institute.
United States: repetition is the mother of wisdom
It becomes even comical, the effort with which Barack Obama, president of the reputation of wise, reproduced the strategy of his predecessor on the Afghan question, that he considered himself as simple.
When he eventually leave sweat its doctrine so eagerly awaited, it turned out that he had in carbon paper since the Iraqi scenario of Bush three years ago.
Not content to use in the text itself several times " as in Iraq, " he has not hesitated, moreover, to use the title of the speech by Bush in January 2007 as the title of his own speech: " A new way forward "
At the same time, he has personally criticized the idea of Bush to send new reinforcements in Iraq consumed by the civil war as " irresponsible and a disastrous decision in its consequences. "
The following month, however, have shown that the strategy of Bush, who came from the recommendations of the commanders of campaigns, was the only possible and likely success to the point that the newspapers currently do not speak at all of Iraq.
This has not enhanced the reputation of Bush, however, objectively speaking, it has left his successor a final situation much more favourable than we might hope.
Barack Obama hopes that in Afghanistan, the miracle will happen
Are the commanders of campaigns that have requested an increase in the military contingent, including the commander of the Afghan operation, General Stanley McCristal, which has severely criticized the reluctance of the White House despite the habits of subordination.
He asked 40,000 men in order to make the situation more favourable.
The president has hesitated for three months but in the absence of a better alternative, at least he had defrauded the general of 10,000 soldiers.
He has managed to root out the promise of additional 5,000 from Europe, even if it were about 10,000.
This brings the most problems throughout the strategy of Obama seems to be its intention to withdraw its troops from Afghanistan within 18 months and to complete this process within three years. The doctrine of Obama raises more questions than it answers.
Many doubt the fact that an increase of half will bring the same fruit that progress in Iraq.
Despite the fratricidal wars of recent years, the Iraqi society is relatively well organized and its leaders to honour the agreements.
The Afghan situation is by the exact opposite - we cannot rely on anyone and no treaty is respected.
In these conditions, difficult to prepare Afghan security forces, accustomed to change from day to day depending on what suits them.
The political institutions, although based officially, will remain as a smokescreen behind which will proliferate patriarchal ethnic relations.
It is particularly difficult to balance the interests of various ethnic groups given the lack of clarity about the reports, which are further complicated by the Pakistani and Iranian influences.
Even the foundation of a " quick to act ", which is the aim of the operation, does not appear to be very real.
The time horizon of the Obama strategy makes perplexed by his determination.
In the past eight years, the situation in Afghanistan has worsened and is currently on the brink of chaos.
Only a heart purely romantic and out of the reality can be confident that the small soldiers sent in the tumult of the war for " speedy return to the home " will bring a real miracle.
From a political point of view, set a date for the withdrawal of troops is purely irresponsible because the Taliban will see as the indirect admission of defeat.
The last NATO summit has shown that the will of Europeans to participate in military operations in Afghanistan is moving towards the negative.
European politicians do not know or do not want to explain to their constituents why security in Germany or Italy is linked to a war in the mountains of the Hindu Kush.
Another factor that could radically alter the situation is the development of events related to Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and that the sanctions have no effect on the Iranians, the Americans will face the very difficult issue of a resolution of the problem by the use of military force.
It will respond by example when, according to Obama, America will come to the victorious withdrawal of troops from Afghanistan.
Each solution of this type will, however, a dramatic reversal of the Afghan situation.
The only patch for Obama is the fact that there are three years until the presidential elections and therefore there is still enough time to working on a new strategy, if it proves to be a flop.
The leaders of the bank Goldman Sachs will receive bonuses in cash
The senior leaders of the US bank Goldman Sachs will not receive cash bonuses this year.
The company announced in response to strong criticism of its pay practices.
The group of 30 leaders will receive shares instead of cash, they will not sell within five years.
The actions can be withdrawn to leaders in case they would take too many risks.
According to Reuters, Goldman Sachs is leading the effort to link the rewards with long - term performance on Wall Street.
I suppose that Wall Street is well aware of the overall sense that we need to take, " said the former investment banker Douglas Elliott of JPMorgan
The concern is in the details, he added.
The bank Goldman Sachs has become the target of criticism after being set aside almost $17 billion in premiums for the first three quarters of this year.
For the current year, the total amount of premiums is likely to exceed $20 billion despite the measure announced today, according to Reuters.
With the arrival of the financial crisis, large bonuses in the banking sector have become a sensitive political issue in many countries.
Britain announced Wednesday that it intends to affect a single fee of 50 percent bankers ' bonuses exceeding 25,000 pounds.
France is preparing similar measures.
This year women received the Nobel Prize in all areas except the physical
These are five women, a record number, which received today in Stockholm at the hands of the King of Sweden Charles XVI Gustave the Nobel Prize in the technical disciplines and literature.
In addition to the four scientists there was also the German writer Herta Müller of Romanian origin.
Two American biologists, Elizabeth Blackburn and Carol Greider received with their compatriot Jack Szostak the Nobel Prize for Medicine for their research in the area of chromosomes.
The prize for chemistry was awarded to the Israeli Ada Jonath with the Americans Venkatraman Ramakrishnan and Thomas Steitz for clarifying the structure and function of the ribosome
The last winner received the Nobel Prize in economics, the American Elinor Ostrom with his countryman Oliver Williamson, for their analysis of economic governance.
The only technical discipline that has no winner this year was the physical.
The award was presented today to scientists Charles Kao for his research in the field of optical fibres and George Smith avecWillard Boyle for their invention of CCD chips, which are the basis of all digital cameras, fax or telescopes.
Each winner received the diploma, the Nobel medal and certificate of acquisition of the financial reward.
It reached 10 million Swedish crowns in each category. (approximately 1.1 million euros)
If one of them has several winners, they will share the reward them.
The much - anticipated Nobel Peace Prize has already been released this afternoon in Oslo in Norway to US President Barack Obama.
In his speech, acknowledged the controversial nature of his reward since it is only at the beginning of his journey and that it is in addition to the head of a country engaged in two wars in Iraq and Afghanistan.
In the discharge of its policy he added that in certain situations the war is essential for peace, even if the price is high.
